parameters: Minion: "I've taken a shot, maybe I'll go have a smoke..."
Minion: "Po, Pony-Celes!!"
Pony-Celes: "Good work on your duty. Now, I'll blow you away!"
Minion: "Wait, wait! Listen to me!"
Minion: "Can you help everyone?"
Pony-Celes: "Help everyone?"

Minion: "I want you to help the people who are being forced to undergo
surgery to become combatants."
Minion: "I can't do it alone..."
Pony-Celes: "You mean... betray Zyda-G?"

Minion: "Yeah, I don't want to do this anymore. I've been waiting for
you to come and help."
Minion: "Please, Pony-Celes..."
Pony-Celes: "..."

Minion: "I was forced to become a combatant... I don't want to make
everyone suffer..."
Pony-Celes: "..."
Pony-Celes: "Alright. I'll trust what you're saying."
Minion: "Really?!"
Minion: "Thank you, Pony-Celes!"
Pony-Celes: "So, what should I do?"

Minion: "There's a staircase leading underground in that drain. You
can infiltrate the combatants' headquarters from there."

Minion: "Right now, all the combatants in the headquarters are waiting
for the announcement to deploy."

Minion: "No matter how strong you are, it's impossible to take on all
the combatants here..."

Pony-Celes: "But I can't just stand by and do nothing. I have to do
something!"
Minion: "Don't rush. I have a plan."
Minion: "Use this!"
You obtained the \i[170]Combatant Suit!
Pony-Celes: "A combatant's outfit?"
Minion: "Yes, exactly."

Minion: "If you wear that outfit, you should be able to infiltrate
without being recognized as Pony-Celes."
Minion: "Once you've infiltrated, head for the innermost room."

Minion: "That's the announcement room, where you can broadcast an
emergency deployment announcement to the entire facility."

Minion: "Once the announcement is made, all combatants should head to
the surface."

Minion: "With the headquarters empty, you can definitely rescue
everyone!"
Pony-Celes: "I see. That's a good plan!"
Minion: "But... there's one problem."

Minion: "You need the captain's card key to use the announcement room.
Only the captain can make an emergency deployment announcement."
Pony-Celes: "So I need to steal it from the captain."
Minion: "You're aware of the risk involved."

Pony-Celes: "It's definitely easier than taking on all the combatants
in the headquarters."

Minion: "You're reliable... But you probably won't need to steal it
from the captain."

Minion: "I've heard that the card key is kept in a drawer in the
captain's private room."

Minion: "The captain is currently out. Once you're in the room, search
for it and find it."
Pony-Celes: "The captain's room, got it!"
Minion: "It's really a relief that you came here. I'm grateful!"

Pony-Celes: "Hehe, it's too early to thank me. Let's wait until
everything goes smoothly."
